# PAD::STOP_CONTROL_SHAKE

## Summary
Stops the given Pad, assigned to a Control, from shaking

## Parameters
* **CONTROL_TYPE** control

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
control: see IS_CONTROL_ENABLED
